reviews.text: very flavoured rice noodle soup, not every day meal though because it is very salty.

This rice noodle shop got many branches that made high accessibility to most people. The food quality is quite standard that I couldn't tell any difference between shops. One of the HK culture that u can choose your own favorite from a wide varieties of meat, fish balls, vegetarian options. Famous of its Sichuan spicy soup that u can also choose different spicy levels too
Seems like this is the only mixian chain which serves vegetarian soup based mixian in HK.

reviews.text: 非一般所謂雲南米線。不試，不入口實難與油腴浮湯滿碗可比。熱，滑，爽入腸道。可以一試！
都知道土匪雞翼需時，1952落單十隻雞翼，半個鐘都未有…… 都有一半係坐唔滿，而2020問進度嗰陣竟然叫我下次唔好嗌土匪雞翼…… 我下次唔會咁嗌㗎喇。

食過最難食的米線, 芽菜冇洗有泥土味道, 湯底咸到腎衰竭, 腐竹冇浸就煮硬到橡膠咁。
Worst of the kind, sprout definitely not washed I can taste the dirt with just one bite. The soup is so salty thats why I suspect I've got renal failure afterwards. Yuba is probably cook in a rush, it is so raw that make me feel like chewing rubber.
味道還不錯，也不算太貴，還可以吧
地方寬敞，但座位舒適，可能是故意的，讓你不能久坐，食品質量可以，服務一般。
